  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You vow to destroy your target with every fiber of your being. As part of casting this jutsu, you may move up to your movement speed toward the target. Movement as a result of this jutsu does not trigger reactions. Make a melee Taijutsu attack against the target, dealing your weapon's damage + 10d12. On a hit, you may also choose to force a target hit by this attack to make a Strength saving throw or be knocked back 100 feet. If a creature collides with a solid object, their movement is stopped, and they take falling damage equal to the distance they would have fallen.</p><p>A creature who is reduced to 0 hit points as a result of this jutsu has some vital organ cut in two, whether it be the heart, brain, or other organ.</p><p>If you would target an Unnatural Being with this attack, you make this attack at advantage, gain 3 additional damage dice on a hit, and they make their saving throw at disadvantage.</p>",
